{"tid":122823,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【三點九沈大師】大師：未必一下落","createTime":"2017-02-16T10:49:54.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-16T13:44:26.000Z","uid":62896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"4f8cd612bd80aedc9ce88383e76726a869679c3f","tid":122823,"uid":62896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T10:49:54.000Z","msg":"好啦三點九沈大師既時間。個市繼續夾24000, 但係就會係到 [廊]下先。雖然我係睇淡後市, 我都相信呢啲位會插返一口。 但都要預反過去眾頂嘅時候未必一下落, 可能落一下落去, 再抽反上黎爆多一口頂。 先至~先至~ 真正做頂都唔定。 但係黎到呢一刻都無辦法, 如果大家係部署上未拿捏得到, 不如靠邊站。要追貨我覺得就要好小心, 真係唔好亂咁追。亦都要預一樣野, 依家淨反可以托市大藍籌唔多。 只係淨反隻941, 你可以常試下。 就用隻941作為你要博就用佢博。 但你要留意啲 鞍鋼 馬鋼 個啲幅圖已經好曳。 會唔會就係指數頂住既時間, 呢啲第一浸升上黎既資源股, 就開始散緊水啦。 咁呢個你地要留意住!"},{"pid":"a1f64bd0bdce5f4c7365f3e67334e3222e5c3335","tid":122823,"uid":65140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T11:01:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/af4207.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Faf4207.jpg&h=df543151&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/4b9d1d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F4b9d1d.jpg&h=7bbbd522&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/a7b3bf.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fa7b3bf.jpg&h=c26bc1c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/d7e817.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2Fd7e817.jpg&h=dccc124f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"33394343ae8d233f4199e10664455b3e401f5ef6","tid":122823,"uid":65140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-16T11:01:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/images/91231b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fphotouploads.com%2Fimages%2F91231b.jpg&h=c9f42e52&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"http://photouploads.com/ima